2. the person eating pineapple is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the car is the person eating apricot##1
4. the person playing billiard is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
6. the fisherman is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Job           | journalist    | fisherman  |
| Food   | pineapple       | apricot    |
